        <num>CCP 4903</num>
        <heading>4903.  Delay for answering in parish and city courts</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4903.  Delay for answering in parish and city courts
The defendant shall answer within ten days of the service of citation, except that when the citation is served through the secretary of state, the delay, as to all defendants, shall be fifteen days after service.</p>
        </content>
